# Format: type(scope): concise summary
#
# Allowed types:
#   feat      new ETF pool capability
#   fix       bug fix
#   data      data source, schema, or quality change
#   docs      documentation only
#   test      tests only
#   refactor  internal code change without behavior change
#   perf      performance improvement
#   build     dependency or packaging change
#   ci        CI/CD change
#   chore     repository maintenance
#   revert    revert an earlier commit
#
# Common scopes: data, tushare, screening, config, cli, docs, git
# Scope is optional. Keep the first line at 72 characters or fewer.
# Use the body to explain why when the subject is not sufficient.
